{
  "npc_id": "qiao",
  "greetings": [
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_morning",
      "text": "锦绣年华须珍惜，$[PLAYER_NAME]！这么早就来逛街了？",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "清晨",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_morning_warm",
      "text": "早安，$[PLAYER_NAME]！今日云霞似锦，定是个好日子。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "清晨",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 4,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_afternoon",
      "text": "午后阳光正好，$[PLAYER_NAME]。我这儿的绣品又添了几幅新花样，来瞧瞧？",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "午后",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_evening",
      "text": "傍晚的霞光最入画，$[PLAYER_NAME]。你看那天边的云，像不像一匹锦缎？",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "傍晚",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_night",
      "text": "夜深了，$[PLAYER_NAME]。我还在赶制这批锦缎呢，客人催得紧。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "夜晚",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_night_warm",
      "text": "夜晚的绣活儿最出活儿，$[PLAYER_NAME]。这么晚还来看我，感动呢。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "夜晚",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 4,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_spring",
      "text": "春暖花开，$[PLAYER_NAME]！这季节的绣线颜色最鲜亮。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "春",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_summer",
      "text": "夏日的绣布最难处理，$[PLAYER_NAME]。得在清晨或傍晚才能上手。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "夏",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_autumn",
      "text": "秋天是收获的季节，$[PLAYER_NAME]。我新织的锦缎用了秋叶的颜色。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "秋",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_winter",
      "text": "冬日绣活儿，$[PLAYER_NAME]。围炉刺绣，最是惬意。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "冬",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_mist",
      "text": "薄雾蒙蒙，$[PLAYER_NAME]。这天气最适合绣云雾纹样了。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "薄雾",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_dense",
      "text": "浓云似海，$[PLAYER_NAME]！我正愁没灵感，这云海来得正好。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "浓云",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_tide",
      "text": "大潮涌动，$[PLAYER_NAME]！这气势若能绣出来，定是绝世佳作！",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "大潮",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_greet_high_heart",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]，你每次来都让我灵感涌动，真想绣一幅你的模样。",
      "favor_min": 150,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 6,
      "heart_max": 10
    }
  ],
  "small_talks": [
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_craft",
      "text": "刺绣讲究的是心静，$[PLAYER_NAME]。一针一线皆有情。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_art",
      "text": "好的绣品要有灵气，$[PLAYER_NAME]。用心绣出来的东西，才能打动人。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_color",
      "text": "色彩搭配是关键，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。你看这云海的颜色，就是最好的调色盘。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_cloud",
      "text": "云海的每一刻都不一样，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。我想把它的美永远留住。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_story",
      "text": "每一幅绣品背后都有一个故事，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。你愿意听听我的故事吗？",
      "favor_min": 50,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 2,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_feeling",
      "text": "和你聊天的时候，$[PLAYER_NAME]$，我总觉得绣出来的花纹都更生动了几分。",
      "favor_min": 100,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 4,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_heart_high",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]$，你在我眼里，就像这云海一样——温柔又让人沉醉。",
      "favor_min": 150,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 6,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_inspiration",
      "text": "好针法需日积月累，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。但灵感这东西，说来就来。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_season",
      "text": "四季都有独特之美，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。春花秋叶，夏云冬雪，都是我绣不完的题材。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_st_tide",
      "text": "大潮的气势太磅礴了，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。我得好好想想怎么表现。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "大潮",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    }
  ],
  "farewells": [
    {
      "id": "qiao_farewell_1",
      "text": "慢走，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。有空常来坐坐，看我绣花也是一种享受。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_farewell_2",
      "text": "那我继续绣了，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。期待下次见面。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_farewell_3",
      "text": "记得常来，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。好的绣品需要懂得欣赏的人来看。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_farewell_high",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]$，你一走我反而更想你了……这话怎么说出口呢。",
      "favor_min": 100,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 4,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_farewell_morning",
      "text": "清晨的时光最珍贵，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。我也得抓紧绣活了。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "清晨",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_farewell_evening",
      "text": "傍晚的光线最适合看绣品，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。可惜你要走了。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "傍晚",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "qiao_farewell_night",
      "text": "夜深了，$[PLAYER_NAME]$。路上小心，早些休息。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "夜晚",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    }
  ]
}
